high_descs: Turn right and walk until you are just past the stove on your right and then turn right and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the green scrubby sponge.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the sponge on the plate you see in there.
Pick up the plate with the sponge on it and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right.
Put the plate down near the edge of the right side a little above the corner closest to us please.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a sponge on it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick the green sponge up from the counter.
Turn around and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the sponge in the bowl in the fridge.
Pick the bowl up out of the fridge and shut the door.
Turn around and stand at the left end of the white table.
Put the bowl down on the table in front of the stool on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a sponge in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and face the kitchen counter to the left of the stove
Pick up a sponge off of the kitchen counter
Turn around and then walk to your left to face the fridge
Open the fridge and put the sponge in the pan
Pick up the pan with a sponge in it
Turn around and keep walking, then turn to the white table on the right
Set the pan with the sponge down on the table
anns.task_desc: Pick up a pan with a sponge in it from the fridge and set it down on the table
